Phrase: We came to the top of Senbon Torii in order to get to Hinayashiki where Miyako is waiting for us.
Yoshino, who had been unwell, seemed to be in excellent health after drinking that dubious water. Yuuzen's charm must have worked.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: The magic power is even stronger than when I came here to inspect the house. The master of Hinayashiki may have sensed our movement.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Even if it sensed us, how could it see us from the other side? I think it's difficult because the Gate is closed.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Even if ya can't see through these Gates, ya can still put 'something to replace the eyes'

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: What? What do you mean by 'something to replace the eyes'?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Like a sorcery that allows a living person to attach something to body and grants vision from a distance. Most people use objects, like dolls or hair ornaments. But there are very rare ones that blend in 'inside' a person.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Yes, for example, using smoke... or water.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: You don't mean, there could be something in Yoshino's body?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I'm talking about the possibility. The curse that Miyako couldn't get rid of may still be in Yoshino's body. I tried to find out when I gave her water to drink, but I couldn't make sure.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Nishiki's curse is really tatty. What an insidious...

Name: Versailles
Phrase: 'It's a matter of the user. At least Miss Yoshino doesn't use that kind of magic.

Name: Putra
Phrase: What about Miyako?

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Miyako is...

Name: Versailles
Phrase: She sometimes uses it.

Name: Putra
Phrase: She uses it!?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: It's not whether you use it or not, but when and how you use it that matters. Miyako will use the art properly when she needs it.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Besides, even Yoshino had used some bad arts...".

Name: Putra
Phrase: Hey, what was that sound?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: There was a sudden increase in magical activity... I wonder if something happened in the Torii maze?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Everyone, we're in trouble! There's a huge influx of monsters coming from down there!

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: They're boiling over from where there's no Mist. Somehow they're heading straight towards us.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Everyone calm down. Don't panic at this level. Even if there is no fog, Monsters can still be summoned. They probably came out of the torii.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Yes, Putra, here's the problem. How many torii are there in this Senbon Torii?

Name: Putra
Phrase: Well, it's called Senbon Torii, so...

Name: Putra
Phrase: Many, so many!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Yes! That's so smart of you, Putra! That means a lot of monsters are coming from a lot of torii!

Name: Putra
Phrase: Vivienne, it's time to test our original formation.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Let's go with 'Suicidal Putra'. I'll cover the rear and wait for the right moment. Putra will just charge into the enemy line in the meantime.

Name: Putra
Phrase: That's right! Let's show the monsters we mean business!

Name: Putra
Phrase: What's the matter? They're not even looking at me, are they?

Name: Putra
Phrase: Are they scared of my intimidation?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: No, they're not.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Look. The monsters are heading straight for Yuuzen.

Name: Putra
Phrase: It's true! They don't even look at Queensway or Yakutsk.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: They're only after Yuuzen. They must be reacting to Yuuzen's magic.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: This is what happens the moment I try to open the gate, huh. It seems that the sorceress over there are more skillful than I thought.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: They're only after Yuuzen. They are too smart to be monsters. Probably some kind of shikigami used by the sorceress.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Nah, they're not as bad as shikigami. I can handle this many of them.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino can help too.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I appreciate the sentiment, but you can't do it. You don't even exist in their dimension.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Rikaibunou. It's a bit too difficult to understand, indeed.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Meaning your magic and sorceries won't work on them.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Understood.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: These are neither monsters nor shikigami, but sorcery itself. It's not reacting to my sorcery, but to the art of breaking barriers.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: The sorceress doesn't want the gate to be opened. She anticipated that I would use magic here. The master of the Hinayashiki must have set a double trap in anticipation of me using said art here.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: What's interesting about this... is that the trap is really malicious. The user doesn't hesitate to kill people with sorcery.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: But this is not so tough. If you think you can beat me with this, you're mistaken.

A crowd of monsters surrounds Yuuzen, paying no attention to anything else.\nIn the face of the eerie things that are "neither monsters nor shikigami, but sorcery itself", Yuzen casted a powerful sorcery so rapidly that Yoshino could not react.
-The power of the sorcery was so strong that it instantly annihilated the crowd of demons gathered on the mountaintop.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Amazing... All those monsters disappeared without a trace...

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: She didn't cast any arts, did she? Wasn't she talking to Yoshino just before the technique was activated?

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Regardless if it's magic or sorcery, it's impossible to activate such a powerful art without doing anything. Yuuzen must have already prepared the formation on this mountaintop beforehand.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: 'It makes sense, but it's not easy. How many people in this world can use that much arts...?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: 'I win this time. This was a lousy deception between two people of bad character.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Where the opponent doesn't like it, there is a weakness. The sorceress' way is to fight so as not to expose that weakness.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino doesn't understand it at all. Yoshino is a sorceress, but I couldn't notice anything...

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: The first barrier has been cleared. Now the trap at the Gate has also been dispelled. I will now pave the way to Hinayashiki. Conductor, please buy me some time so they don't get in the way.
That's of course, but... why do you need us to buy some time?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: ...It's going to be a little while before I can reuse my sorcery. I exhausted a lot of power myself.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yuuzen, did you get cursed?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: What curse!?

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Is this an attack from Hinayashiki!?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: It's nothing to be fussed about. This level of curse is to be expected.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: But it's affecting you quite a bit...

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I told ya. I risked my life. I'm lucky to have succeeded in breaking the enchantment alive.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: All that sweat... Isn't she on a worse condition than Yoshino?

Name: Putra
Phrase: What are we going to do? Do we go back and have a look?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: If that's the case, it doesn't make sense for Yuuzen to try so hard. If Yuuzen says she can do it, we should finish it.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Without Yuuzen, Miyako can't be saved. If we miss this chance, there will be no next time.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: The little fox is right. We continue as planned. Things have been going according to plan so far in the first place. There's no need to change strategy here.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Let's give Yuuzen a rest. We'll all go to the black torii gate to prevent bad things from coming.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: But you know what, Yuuzen? Yoshino is still not convinced.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: What did ya say?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Right now Yuuzen doesn't trust us yet. Yuuzen has been fighting alone since a while ago.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: That's not good. Let's make sure that we are all in good relations with each other. Yuuzen is going to fight together with Yoshino and the others from now on.
Yoshino said some unexpected words to Yuuzen, who was weakened by the curse. Inside the black torii... in Hinayashiki, an evil presence was still leaking out of that place.
